<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Privacy Policy</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  }
  /* Modal Overlay */
  .modal-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 999;
  }

  /* Modal Content */
  .modal-content {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 20px;
    max-height: 90%;
    min-width: 90%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  .modal-title {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #000;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .small-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #999;
    line-height: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .close-btn {
    background-color: #ccc;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .close-btn:hover {
    background-color: #aaa;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="privacyModal">
  <div class="modal-content">
    <div class="modal-title">Privacy Policy</div>

    <p>Last updated: <script>document.write(new Date().toLocaleDateString());</script></p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      • Game scores and progress (stored locally on your device)<br>
      • App usage analytics (anonymous)<br>
      • Ad interaction data (managed by Google AdMob)<br>
      • Device information for ad serving
    </p>

    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>
      • To save your game progress and high scores<br>
      • To improve app performance and user experience<br>
      • To display relevant advertisements<br>
      • To provide technical support when requested
    </p>

    <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
    <p>
      • Game data is stored locally on your device<br>
      • We do not store personal information on our servers<br>
      • Analytics data is anonymized and aggregated<br>
      • We use industry-standard security measures
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      • Google AdMob for advertisement serving<br>
      • Google Analytics for app usage statistics<br>
      • These services have their own privacy policies<br>
      • You can opt out of personalized ads in your device settings
    </p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      Our app is designed to be family-friendly. We do not knowingly
      collect personal information from children under 13. All
      advertisements are family-safe and appropriate for all ages.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      • Delete app data by uninstalling the app<br>
      • Opt out of personalized ads in device settings<br>
      • Contact us with privacy concerns<br>
      • Request information about data we collect
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us
      at: <a href="mailto:alidiplana@gmail.com">alidiplana@gmail.com</a>
    </p>

    <p class="small-text">
      This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. We will
      notify users of any material changes through app updates.
    </p>

    <button class="close-btn" onclick="document.getElementById('privacyModal').style.display='none'">
      Close
    </button>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
